Package it.polimi.ingsw.network

Class RemoteAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.network.RemoteAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class RemoteAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is used to represent sudo-actions on client's side. This way, the client can communicate to the server without having full access to the model (in fact the infos available through this class are limited to the ones that the client has necessary access to).
